{"tid":610552,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國體育局:輸0-6的不是國家隊，只是雜牌軍，真正國家隊未出場","createTime":"2018-03-30T05:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T19:15:07.000Z","uid":14918,"like":254,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"00d1a86e432385c1c8c216e6b4b193512b08aaa7","tid":610552,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"北京時間3月30日消息，國家體育總局召開全國青少年體育工作電視電話會議，據足球報消息，會議上，<span style=\"color: red;\">國家體育總局副局長趙勇給中國隊0比6負於威爾士隊「定性」。他指出，那不是國家隊，那是雜牌軍</span>，隊員都是來自各俱樂部的，中超裡面你要打我，我要打你，怎麼指望他們團結？趙勇指出，今後若非參加奧運等比賽，所有中國之隊都是國家集訓隊。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本次會議還透露兩個信息：一是今後青少年比賽都要直播，而且是電視直播，不是網絡直播；二是將來還要建立足球評級制度。不過，如何對足球評級本次會議沒有進行詳細說明，只是表示青少司正在草擬。"},{"pid":"5a525eeb1b30553f94dc71f3888dc87595d1fe75","tid":610552,"uid":34394,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed22724d118f0c7f476a79fbc56145b2301fefe5","tid":610552,"uid":19542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba6eaeaad6144259756920d590c5217882fe36c","tid":610552,"uid":14918,"like":265,"dislike":2,"score":263,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"國家隊不是國家隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n厲害了，我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/283/w650h433/20180323/qXgy-fysnevm1247124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F283%2Fw650h433%2F20180323%2FqXgy-fysnevm1247124.jpg&h=b705a873&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a31bdce992aaa5d4945aab65ec39365814f2a52e","tid":610552,"uid":582,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:15:14.000Z","msg":"同d功夫撚一樣🤣"},{"pid":"d2fd122cf839990e3b7557952b1c62a023f723