的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向中國，最好一開場就給主隊一張紅牌<br />\n10.鄭智帶球，你不能幾個後衛去攔截，要讓鄭智順利射門<br />\n11.你不能鏟鄭智<br />\n12.你進的球前要把中國每個隊員都過一遍，最好把兩個門柱都過一遍，然後再把球踢進大門，這樣才是真水平，否則中國認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.你後衛在本方禁區不能開大腳<br />\n14.你要允許中國的教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，中國迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。中國迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},{"pid":"012cba7a1a4b2a5418f883479139f59a14441880","tid":610552,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"香港係邊撚到？"},{"pid":"5947322da7b1454812425ebd5d4907432f5b84ac","tid":610552,"uid":21708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827a4a104a95277ad98a74ee9b38bc5181486a04","tid":610552,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"其他聯賽唔係？ <br />\n不過中国人有人愛國架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢有知識都唔愛國"},{"pid":"3ce6dc27ece0de437c5c778ff072630ad95596bb","tid":610552,"uid":141197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"這國家不是我的"},{"pid":"68b0beab600102d69a0ddbcb08e282b8be93d48c","tid":610552,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bb527bac7db0546801040bc2a8f5f1b0338b3f","tid":610552,"uid":40588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f8067070f65fa5a5e79bb031fe7bd3c7a7231e0","tid":610552,"uid":163031,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"邊有國家會話自己球員係雜牌軍咁仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"阿根庭"},{"pid":"b786e97b79616dde3c6e7561a22aaf27e910f41f","tid":610552,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0